Uses of Package
org.openwms.common.comm.osip

  • Packages that use org.openwms.common.comm.osip 
    Package Description
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip
    This package contains all types to handle OSIP telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.app
    Contains Spring configuration files and other lifecycle relevant types for OSIP.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.err
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP ERR telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.err.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP ERR telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.impl
    Contains default implementations and bean instances to be extended and overridden.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.locu
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP LOCU telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.locu.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP LOCU telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.req
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP REQ telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.req.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP REQ telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.res
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP RES telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.res.spi
    Contains types and default implementations to extend the RES_ telegram handling.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.synq
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP SYNQ telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.synq.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP SYNQ telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.sysu
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP SYSU telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.sysu.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP SYSU telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.upd
    Contains types responsible for dealing with OSIP UPD telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.upd.spi
    Contains types and default implementations to extend the UPD telegram handling.
    org.openwms.common.comm.osip.upd.tcp
    Contains types to serialize and deserialize OSIP UPD telegrams and messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.router
    Contains implementations following the Message Router pattern.
    org.openwms.common.comm.transformer
    Contains types that act as Message Transformer components.
  • Classes in org.openwms.common.comm.osip used by org.openwms.common.comm.osip 
    Class Description
    OSIPComponent
    A OSIPComponent.
    OSIPHeader
    A OSIPHeader represents the header part of a OSIP telegram message.
    OSIPHeader.Builder  
    OSIPSerializer
    A OSIPSerializer is able to serialize OSIP messages into Strings that can be sent over the wire.
    Payload
    A Payload is the abstract superclass of all messages sent to subsystems like PLC or ERP.
    ResponseHeader
    A ResponseHeader.
    ResponseHeader.Builder
